			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="content-wrapper">
				<h2 class="section-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
				<div class="grid-wrapper" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">How do I book an airport transfer in Puerto Vallarta?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							WhatsApp us at +52 5644166523 or fill out our contact form. Confirmation within 15–30 minutes.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Which airport serves Puerto Vallarta?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Licenciado Gustavo Díaz Ordaz International Airport (PVR). We serve all terminals and private
							aviation areas.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Do you go to Sayulita or Punta Mita?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Yes. We serve Sayulita, Punta Mita, Bucerías, Nuevo Vallarta, and all Riviera Nayarit destinations.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Are transfers 100% private?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Absolutely. No shared vehicles. Your exclusive private transfer, just the way you want it.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section bg-white">
			<div class="content-wrapper" style="text-align:center;">
				<h2 class="section-heading">Book Your Puerto Vallarta Airport Transfer</h2>
				<p class="primary-text grey-color" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
					Available 24/7. No hidden fees. Reply in 15 minutes.
				</p>
				<a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="cta-button w-button">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
				<span style="display:inline-block;width:1rem;"></span>
				<a href="/contact" class="cta-button w-button" style="background:#333;">Send a Request</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<div class="footer-section-wrapper">
				<div class="content-wrapper">
					<div class="footer-content-wrapper">
						<div class="footer-top-content">
							<div class="footer-logo-social">
								<a href="/" class="brand w-nav-brand">
									<span class="brand-logo-text footer-brand-logo-text">ELITE RIDE MEXICO</span>
								</a>
								<div class="footer-text">
									Private airport transfers across Mexico. Premium SUVs, bilingual drivers, available 24/7.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="divider"></div>
						<div class="footer-bottom-content">
							<div class="footer-links-wrapper">
								<h2 class="heading">Pages</h2>
								<a href="/" class="footer-nav-link">Home</a>
								<a href="/about" class="footer-nav-link">About</a>
								<a href="/our-fleet" class="footer-nav-link">Our Fleet</a>
								<a href="/contact" class="footer-nav-link">Contact Us</a>
							</div>
							<div class="footer-links-wrapper">
